for Poverty Reduction (REP-PoR) aims to affect broad-based interventions in the energy sector, focusing on Asia Pacific countries. The emphasis is on harnessing energy effectively to meet developmental targets laid out in the Millennium Development Goals. As a first step to achieve", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "56476c96-0f8e-4fec-81ac-e750475e6af7": {"__data__": {"id_": "56476c96-0f8e-4fec-81ac-e750475e6af7", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/energy-and-poverty-viet-nam", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "Energy and Poverty in Viet Nam", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/energy-and-poverty-viet-nam", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "e20cb73be8c1bd519aae20745dc523944bb8818122aa2ae7d7de404b961cd710"}}, "hash": "e20cb73be8c1bd519aae20745dc523944bb8818122aa2ae7d7de404b961cd710", "text": "the objectives of REP-PoR, this publication reports on Viet Nam\u2019s energy sector and its linkages to poverty concerns, gaps therein, and modalities for overcoming the same. It aims to facilitate the inclusion of a strong energy component to Viet Nam\u2019s socio- economic development programmes. US$ 5", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "f78b16aa-d953-449e-90fe-700bb01fb95c": {"__data__": {"id_": "f78b16aa-d953-449e-90fe-700bb01fb95c", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https: