V of replacement cost Some of the equipment associated with the project will be of shorter life than the project and will need to be replaced periodically.", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "4725b1e9-a476-431a-b200-cb9f66a6f99d": {"__data__": {"id_": "4725b1e9-a476-431a-b200-cb9f66a6f99d", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/energy-costing-tool-user-guide", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "Energy Costing Tool: User Guide", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/energy-costing-tool-user-guide", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "d9defe02fb0e5c8103bf1ded47a143cd95c0a9a517ad133ee1a3c78d9f046f50"}, "2": {"node_id": "11637645-d813-4d71-adc3-a3e7c2b8c6ca", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/energy-costing-tool-user-guide", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "38a1755346929d3559c8c835a05f505db437601f946ed006671ea4c11220f2e7"}}, "hash": "8537ff9ff1e98298f2541bee6d116e12ff8e261df5622ef838bcc5e824c3b979", "text": "The present value of the cost of replacements (KR) is estimated as follows: NR PV(KRAnn, deff, NR) = KR * \u2211 1 \u2215 (1+deff) NR NR=1 Where: deff = (1+d) Le \u2013 1 = Effective discount rate NR = (L/LE) \u2212 1 L = Life of the project Le = Life of the replacement device PV of operation and maintenance cost (O&M) Present value of annual operations and maintenance costs are estimated as follows: L PV (O&MAnn, d, n) = \u2211 O&MAnnn \u2215 (1+d) n n=1 16 Energy costing tool user\u2019s guide If the O&M costs are constant, then: PV (O&MAnn, d, n) = PV (1Ann, d, L) * O&MAnn PV of fuel cost The present value of annual fuel costs for a given level of capacity utilization are estimated as follows: L PV (FAnn, d, n) = \u2211 FAnnn \u2215 (1+d) n n=1 If the fuel costs are constant, then: PV(FAnn, d, n) = PV (1Ann, d, L) * Fann Life cycle cost (LCC) The present value of different cost components (as above) is summed up to obtain the life cycle cost of installing and operating the project. The cost of disposal can also be included depending on the type of projects and the needs of decision making. LCC = PV( ) + PV(Ku) + PV(KR) + PV(O&M) + PV(F) Annualized life cycle cost (ALC) The annual cost of installing and operating a project is estimated as follows: ALC = LCC / PV (1Ann, d, L) 4. Instructions for using the Energy Costing Tool 17 4 Instructions for using the Energy Costing Tool 4.1 Colour code for using the Tool The user needs to follow the colour code outlined below (Table 1) while using the Tool:", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "be315ae2-820d-4e77-bcca-66bc4571011c": {"__data__": {"id_": "be315ae2-820d-4e77-bcca-66bc4571011c", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/energy-costing-tool-user-guide", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "Energy Costing Tool: User Guide", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/energy-costing-tool-user-guide", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher