mates are more appropriate and adequate for capturing cost implications. As with Table 7, Table 8 contains definitions of units of measurement for various parameters in the top few rows. The units of measurement have been given for input fuel, capacity, electricity, etc. For exam- ple, the unit of capacity for smaller plants (e.g. biomass gasifier power) has been defined in kW, where as it is MW for larger plants (grid coal). Similarly, the currency size is \u2018million\u2019 for larger plants. The next few rows have linked cells from the \u2018Design parameters\u2019 worksheet. TABlE 8: Data for estimating unit cost of electricity production Note: Feathered edges indicate that only a portion of the full table is shown here.", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "e1a712b2-e6d3-473b-b186-852d970f45d9": {"__data__": {"id_": "e1a712b2-e6d3-473b-b186-852d970f45d9", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/energy-costing-tool-user-guide", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "Energy Costing Tool: User Guide", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/energy-costing-tool-user-guide", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "f0ccc71d5e328d123dcdedea49d469a364837f83e7a5f45b17ada515a7dc12e6"}, "2": {"node_id": "9afa4161-5533-4460-b39b-969ca50e5d10", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/energy-costing-tool-user-guide", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Develo