ion provided in the blues cells is not relevant for the base year. It is important to remember that the total share in each column (if selected) always has to equal 100. \u2022\ufffdAccess to electricity technologies \u2013 Target for 2010: Based on the information available for the base year, the 2010 targets need to be fixed. The information provided in blue cells, such as the elec- tricity generation cost/kWh of each technology, can be used in arriving at the targets. For example, prioritization could be based on a least cost principle. The contribution from the existing grid is an estimated number, which depends on the", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "d151148f-f2d3-4b3d-9a65-70d0ef2c14e2": {"__data__": {"id_": "d151148f-f2d3-4b3d-9a65-70d0ef2c14e2", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/energy-costing-tool-user-guide", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "Energy Costing Tool: User Guide", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/energy-costing-tool-user-guide", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "51849a75839765ee50b1a243e8038471f1fc833ed820d8e5e32d1fd3d918a4d2"}, "3": {"node_id": "0a8b6d71-7f2f-44b2-824f-f2135def3ea3", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/energy-costing-tool-user-guide", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "e15e728f73d49cc07ee87167974e708dd89fd9b4d3c2eba4e4ac23070d4