ing future targets, is the same as that described above. Only the sources of information may be different.", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "2dc95f37-6bca-4cba-ab55-40ed8792d20c": {"__data__": {"id_": "2dc95f37-6bca-4cba-ab55-40ed8792d20c", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/energy-costing-tool-user-guide", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "Energy Costing Tool: User Guide", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/energy-costing-tool-user-guide", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "a7bfb939b43666b324794b420990d4bfcb216c02674df09b86048d527f37b954"}, "2": {"node_id": "bcf0f151-9edd-4cdb-9921-0f8d3de6d2ed", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/energy-costing-tool-user-guide", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "c4564370cda8378cbedc1cff5219a49a9fda7cda42a35711d2320d68b055cc40"}}, "hash": "c93a7acac31fc128e0a579714582be0d440e315e96e4f9eb055985f070fe4b04", "text": "Only the sources of information may be different. 40 Energy costing tool user\u2019s guide TABlE 18: MDG access targets for heating energy and systems Access to heat energy for agro-processing, micro-industry (Only rural) (%) Term years Rural 1 Rural 2 Rural 3 Rural 4 2006 0 0 0 0 2010 0 0 0 0 2015 0 0 0 0 2006 Fuels Cost/GJ Rural 1 Rural 2 Rural 3 Rural 4 Kerosene 6.83 0 0 0 0 Sustainable biomass 1.95 0 0 0 0 Fuel oil 12.57 